### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### DOCX to PDF (replace bucket and keys)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/convert/docx-to-pdf
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": {
    "bucket": "your-bucket",
    "key": "input/docx/docx_smoke_001.docx"
  },
  "output": {
    "bucket": "your-bucket",
    "keyPrefix": "output/pdf/"
  }
}

### PDF to images
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/convert/pdf-to-images
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": {
    "bucket": "your-bucket",
    "key": "input/pdf/pdf_smoke_001.pdf"
  },
  "output": {
    "bucket": "your-bucket",
    "keyPrefix": "output/images/pdf_smoke_001/"
  },
  "render": {
    "dpi": 150,
    "format": "png",
    "maxPages": 50,
    "pageRange": null
  }
}
